## Why This Is Asked
Tests end-to-end integration of AWS AI services with a clean event-driven pattern, including common NLU tasks (sentiment, themes) and a custom-entities layer for domain knowledge. It also probes data handling, privacy, and operational trade-offs.

## Key Concepts
